alerts.description: Es treten oberhalb 1000 m Sturmböen mit Geschwindigkeiten bis 80 km/h (22m/s, 44kn, Bft 9) aus südwestlicher Richtung auf.

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: < 80 km/h; Wind direction: south-west

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: ~ 55 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 65 km/h
